Revision history for DBIx::Class::DeploymentHandler::CLI

0.3.0  Mon Jan  3 17:43:46 2022 CET

    * Add support for configuration files.
    * Add install_custom and run_custom methods.

0.002  Tue Jan  3 15:43:59 2017 CET

    * Force current mysql_version for SQL::Translator instead of using the
      totally outdated default.
    * Add missing returns to methods to prevent display of implicit return
      values.
    * Add "Best Practices" section to documentation.
    * Handle missing and empty version storage in database_version method.

0.001  Wed Mar  9 10:08:23 2016 CET

        German Perl Workshop 2016 release.


